s=\"lucide lucide-check mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Análisis de inversiones</span></li></ul><a href=\"/s/es/nexa-uruguay/contacto?programa=investor\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium transition-all duration-normal focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] text-[var(--secondary)] bg-transparent hover:bg-[var(--secondary)] hover:text-white h-13 px-8 text-lg rounded-lg mt-8 w-full\">Solicitar consulta</a></article></div></div></div></section><section id=\"por-que\" class=\"bg-[var(--background)] py-16 sm:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"animate-on-scroll mb-12 text-center\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--secondary)]\">Por qué Uruguay</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-tight font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--text)]\" style=\"text-transform:var(--heading-transform)\">Estabilidad, previsibilidad, apertura</h2></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-2\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-8 shadow-card transition-all hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-[var(--secondary)]/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Estabilidad primero</h3><p class=\"text-[var(--text-light)]\">Uruguay combina fortaleza institucional, baja corrupción y estado de derecho predecible.</p><ul class=\"mt-4 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Democracia sólida</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Hub financiero regional</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Grado de inversión</span></li></ul></article></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-3\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-8 shadow-card transition-all hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-[var(--secondary)]/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Oportunidades de inversión</h3><p class=\"text-[var(--text-light)]\">Zonas francas, inmobiliario, agroindustria, tecnología.</p><ul class=\"mt-4 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Zonas francas</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Sector tecnológico en crecimiento</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Inmobiliario en Punta del Este</span></li></ul></article></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-4\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-8 shadow-card transition-all hover:shadow-card-hover\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-[var(--secondary)]/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Calidad de vida</h3><p class=\"text-[var(--text-light)]\">Seguridad, educación, clima, comunidad internacional.</p><ul class=\"mt-4 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Seguridad pública</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Educación pública y privada sólida</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]\"><span class=\"text-[var(--secondary)]\">•</span><span>Playa + ciudad</span></li></ul></article></div></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll\"><aside class=\"mx-auto mt-12 max-w-3xl rounded-lg border-l-4 border-[var(--secondary)] bg-[var(--surface-light)] p-6\"><p class=\"text-sm italic text-[var(--text-light)]\">Uruguay no es barato — es estable. Ese tradeoff es la clave. Si prioriza el costo, Paraguay puede ser mejor opción; se lo diremos.</p></aside></div></div></section><section id=\"proceso\" class=\"bg-[var(--surface-light)] py-16 sm:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"animate-on-scroll mb-12 text-center\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--secondary)]\">Cómo funciona</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-tight font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--text)]\" style=\"text-transform:var(--heading-transform)\">Un proceso claro, paso a paso</h2></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-5\"><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-2\"><div class=\"relative text-center\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] bg-[var(--surface)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.236 1.168l3.413-.998a2 2 0 0 1 1.099.092 10 10 0 1 0-4.777-4.719\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-heading)\">Consulta inicial</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--text-light)]\">Evaluamos su situación y el programa adecuado.</p></div></div><div class=\"animate-on-scroll stagger-3\"><div class=\"relative text-center\"><div class=\"mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--secondary)] bg-[var(--surface)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-check text-[var(--secondary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 